item.title: Whats the new bot..?
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

There are many new bots and ways to create new bots, and any number of cheating communities other than this one.

You yourself could learn to create a bot by spending a few weeks at most learning java, a few weeks at most learning BCEL, and a few weeks writing the actual bot.

Or for a shittier bot, just force methods. Or for a slightly better bot, just force methods and pretend your not (aryan). Or for a slightly better bot, go through some hitherto unthought of way of imitating mouseclicks.

Point being: Who cares if there’s a new bot?
